{"id": 1966, "genre": 1000, "title": "行走江湖，你都有过哪些“注销难”的体验？", "description": "互联网时代的“注册容易注销难”, 有的不光是理发店充值卡的钱没花了这种金钱层面的糟心，个人信息被滥用是很多人对这件事的担心。（题图来自: Pixabay）", "record_count": 7406, "comment_count": 33, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201710191232003G58Ei1rsnXAz4hV.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-10-19T17:00:23Z", "questions": [{"id": 3154, "title": "行走江湖，你都有过哪些“注销难”的体验？", "content": "你都有过哪些“注销难”的体验？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 242550, "content": "平台没有注销入口，或是入口隐蔽，藏在犄角旮旯找起来困难", "image": "img/option/option/20171019000215Pfv2zO46uDHjZChM.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 242551, "content": "霸王条款，根本不支持注销/解绑", "image": "img/option/option/20171019003716CS0bFtGNAPpUnLZD.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 242552, "content": "用福利强行挽留，比如取消信用卡时银行说可以提升额", "image": "img/option/option/20171019000527J0MhSF8ykVNfagvG.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 242553, "content": "真正需要解绑或者注销时，一定要客服人工审核，流程缓慢", "image": "img/option/option/20171019000631kH6nbco7iyGuK9s2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 242554, "content": "平时就算了，解绑还需要上传证件信息验证，担心个人信息安全问题", "image": "img/option/option/201710190116057Zi5ptLlWsOkP1Rb.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 242555, "content": "前面一堆步骤，然后还需要解绑账号关联的app/网站/业务", "image": "img/option/option/20171019004902HwS3N2jzPQmnFRGB.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 242556, "content": "终于可以分手了……需要清空账户余额，通常还不能提现", "image": "img/option/option/20171019012822fMcHBLJQ8IuAhUjq.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 242559, "content": "需要使用初始/常用的邮箱、手机号进行确认，丢手机、换邮箱后难度加倍", "image": "img/option/option/20171019011848nzHu9IDyTCQGrMWj.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}